targets.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("allReqIn"), 1m) AS "GetReq:In", non_negative_derivative(mean("allReqOut"), 1m) AS "GetReq:Out" FROM ( SELECT "snmpInGetRequests"+"snmpInGetNexts" AS "allReqIn", "snmpOutGetRequests"+"snmpOutGetNexts" AS "allReqOut" FROM "snmp.HPLJ" WHERE "agent_host" =~ /^$host$/ AND $timeFilter) WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)

list.label: Printer:
list.name: host
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "snmp.HPLJ" WITH KEY = "agent_host"

list.label: Interface:
list.name: intf
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "ifTable" WITH KEY = "ifDescr" WHERE "agent_host" = '$host'
